Package org.sat4j.specs

Interface ILogAble

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractLauncher, AbstractOptimizationLauncher, BasicLauncher, MUSLauncher
    public interface ILogAble
    Utility interface to catch objects with logging capability (able to log). The interface supersedes the former org.sat4j.minisat.core.ICDCLLogger introduced in release 2.3.2.

    2.3.3
